Title: Where There's Smoke, There's Fire
Description:
If you are finished indulging Ebyssian's associate, I would have us return to more pressing matters. 

Locating Fyrakk is still our primary mission. We cannot continue to delay it.

I have discovered a massive caldera at the western edge of Zaralek. If Fyrakk is still here, then logic dictates that this volcanic area would be his hideout.

Meet us there and we will proceed.
ObjectivesText: Meet Ebyssian and Sabellian outside the Zaqali Caldera.
